{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tag-tsx","path":"/tags/habits/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"jmsbrdy"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"totalCount":2,"edges":[{"node":{"excerpt":"As described in an earlier post, I’ve been using James Clear’s Atomic Habits as a tool over the last few months. The focus on process and incremental gains has been useful, and leaves one with a fairly clear set of steps to work through – unlike many self-improvement books. It got me to thinking, though, how could the same approach be applied to a team or company?","fields":{"slug":"/atomic-habits-for-organisations/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"June 18, 2020","title":"Atomic Habits for organisations","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4883720930232558,"src":"/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/61fd6/the-habit-loop.png","srcSet":"/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/49ddd/the-habit-loop.png 64w,\n/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/62915/the-habit-loop.png 128w,\n/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/61fd6/the-habit-loop.png 256w,\n/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/450e9/the-habit-loop.png 384w,\n/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/bc59e/the-habit-loop.png 512w,\n/static/1c57faf773b37f1216137ab947f70f95/12b05/the-habit-loop.png 836w","sizes":"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px"}}},"staticThumbnail":null}}},{"node":{"excerpt":"Atomic Habits is chock-full of stories of people making transformative changes through the purposeful adoption of new habits: losing weight, professional success, creative output. After reading the book, I was sold: the approach uses what we know about behaviour patterns to hack our brains, aligning the basic urges of our Id with the lofty goals of our Superego. However, what wasn’t obvious was how I should go about choosing these habits in the first place. There wasn’t a clear process laid out in the book, but here I describe one that uses its principles and worked well for me.","fields":{"slug":"/choosing-atomic-habits/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"May 08, 2020","title":"Atomic Habits: what habits do you actually want?","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":0.6808510638297872,"src":"/static/b417134c6a701df4e1b153b069f07ba2/07af2/phrenology.jpg","srcSet":"/static/b417134c6a701df4e1b153b069f07ba2/684c4/phrenology.jpg 64w,\n/static/b417134c6a701df4e1b153b069f07ba2/6d25d/phrenology.jpg 128w,\n/static/b417134c6a701df4e1b153b069f07ba2/07af2/phrenology.jpg 256w,\n/static/b417134c6a701df4e1b153b069f07ba2/57dc6/phrenology.jpg 384w,\n/static/b417134c6a701df4e1b153b069f07ba2/19a28/phrenology.jpg 493w","sizes":"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px"}}},"staticThumbnail":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"tag":"habits"}}}